title: ASHBURY DEMO LAPS
description:
A couple of laps and lens splashes before the demo at Bear Mountain. Riders in order of appearance: Ben Bilocq, Austin Leonard, Cameron Strand, Marie Hucal, Brandon Phillips, Jake Kuzyk, Jordan Small, and Durell Williams.

Shot and edited by Ransacker.
